ActTerritorial Lands Act
SubjectWithdrawal from Disposal of Certain Tracts of Territorial Lands in Nunavut (Kivalliq area) Order
PrecisWITHDRAWAL FROM DISPOSAL OF CERTAIN TRACTS OF TERRITORIAL LANDS IN NUNAVUT (KIVALLIQ AREA) ORDER which withdraws from disposal the surface and subsurface rights to certain lands, for a period of three years, in order to facilitate the conclusion of Aboriginal land agreements.
